    12/4 - NYC
3)  UCLA Anderson Forecast - Keynote address by California
    Governor Gray Davis
    12/5 - LA
4)  UCLA Anderson Forecast - On the Road, Sponsored by Oracle
    12/6 - Bay Area
5)  New York Chapter Holiday Party with Professor Cockrum
    12/6 - NYC
6)  Accenture 2001 C4C Ski Trip
    12/14 to 12/17 - BC, Canada
